K1 – Semantic Search: RAG answers based on PDF content.
Acceptance: Answer must include at least 1 SourceRef.

K2 – Ingestion: Extract text, chunk, and embed PDFs.
Acceptance: PDF ingestion completes without errors.

K3 – Vector Database: Store/search embeddings (similarity, top‑K).
Acceptance: Query returns top‑K chunks.

K4 – RAG Answer with Sources: Answers must show document name and page.
Acceptance: Each answer cites document and page.

K5 – Authentication: Only enterprise accounts via Extranet/OIDC.
Acceptance: Unauthorized users receive 401.

K6 – Logging: Log query, userId, sources, latency.
Acceptance: Each search is logged with all fields.

K7 – Frontend: Next.js  UI for login, query, answer.
Acceptance: User can log in and submit queries.

K8 – PoC Scope: Limited number of documents, simple UI.
Acceptance: Demo runs with restricted set of docs.